<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>qf yạ jndy jạnb ạlṣlyb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- qf yạ jndy jạnb ạlṣlyb ʿnd sẖrwq ạlnwr
 ḥty ʿnd ạnsdạl ạlẓlạm tẖq brbnạ ṣkẖr ạldhwr

[V2]
 ạlqrạr - qf bjwạr ạlṣlyb ạ̉yhạ ạljndy ạljbạr
 sngẖlb ʿn qryb wnrjʿ bạlạ̹ntṣạr

[V3]
 2- qf dạỷmạaⁿ jạnb ạlṣlyb ạ̹ly ạ̹nqḍạʾ ạlnhạr
 kn tẖạbtạaⁿ kdẖạ wạtẖqạaⁿ bʿd dẖy ạlḥrwb ạlạ̹ntṣạr

[V4]
 3- qf yạ jndy bsẖjạʿẗ wạqtḥm ạlạ̉ʿdạʾ
 lyl ʿlyk syhjm swf yạ̉ty ạlnwr bạlbhạʾ

[V5]
 4- qf ḥty yrjʿ rbk yjdk gẖạlbạaⁿ
 mn sẖftyh stsmʿ kfạk qtạlạaⁿ mtʿbạaⁿ

[V6]
 1- qif̊ yā jun̊dī̃̊ jāniba ạlṣãlīb̊
 ʿin̊da sẖurūqi ạlnũwr̊
 ḥatãy̱ ʿin̊da ạn̊sidāli ạlẓãlạm̊
 tẖiq̊ birabĩnā ṣakẖ̊ri ạldũhūr̊

[V7]
 ạlqrạr: qif̊ bijiwāri ạlṣãlīb̊
 ạảyũhā ạl̊jun̊dī̃̊ ạl̊jabãạr̊
 sanagẖ̊libu ʿan̊ qarīb̊
 wanar̊jiʿu biạlạn̊tiṣār̊

[V8]
 2- qif̊ ḥatãy̱ yar̊jiʿa rabũka
 yajid̊ka gẖālibaⁿạ
 min̊ sẖafataẙhi satas̊maʿu
 kafāka qitālạaⁿ mut̊ʿibaⁿạ</lyrics>
